*** Keywords ***
# Actions
Open Page HSL In Browser
    Open Browser    ${BASE_URL}    ${BROWSER}
    Maximize Browser Window
    Wait Until Page Contains Element    ${btn_accept_coocies}

Click Element And Wait
    [Arguments]
    ...    ${element}
